			<span class="kicker"><a href="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/category/series/morning-agenda/">Morning Agenda</a></span>		</div>
				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Stemming Departures at SAC</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Sydney Ember			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-04-02T12:01:25+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">April 2, 2014 8:01 am</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">April 2, 2014 8:01 am</span><button class="button comments-button  theme-kicker" data-skip-to-para-id="">
