<h6 class="kicker"><a href="//dealbook.blogs.nytimes.com/category/ipoofferings/">I.P.O./OFFERINGS Â»</a></h6>
<div class="ru-story">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><img alt="GrubHub Raises Price Range for I.P.O." src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2014/03/25/business/dbpix-grubhub/dbpix-grubhub-square320.jpg" width="75" height="75" border="0" /><span class="title">GrubHub Raises Price Range for I.P.O. <span class="divider">Â |Â </span></span><!-- end .title --> The online food ordering service GrubHub, familiar to legions of office workers, says it expects to price its stock at $23 to $25 a share. <span class="elsewhere"><a href="//dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/04/01/grubhub-raises-price-range-for-i-p-o/">DealBook Â»</a></span></p>
